                                    <div style="width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 10px; background: #EFF6FF; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><i data-lucide="qr-code" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; color: #3B99FC;"></i></div>
